South Africa Power Consumption Climbed 2.5% in May, Production Gained 3.4%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-07T11:05:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/south-africa-power-consumption-climbed-2-5-in-may-production-gained-3-4-.html
South African power consumption
increased by 2.5 percent in May from a year earlier, while
production gained 3.4 percent, Statistics South Africa said in a
statement published on its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  